{"id":232760035,"title":"游","content":"今天沒幾朵雲\n薄藍色的天啊\n妳會不會害羞？\n\n應是閒慵的風景\n卻身不由己\n我望著妳\n偷噙淚\n回首向北\n怒懟微風\n斥她太溫柔\n說這不是遊子應做的夢\n\n陰翳蠢動\n侵吞斗室\n從指尖\n到字簍\n從鼻息\n到季風\n徬徨漏網\n悲苦蔽光\n我佛慈悲\n能否替我安葬？\n\n我能為妳哭出幾片浮雲\n也請妳為我\n留方陽光。","excerpt":"今天沒幾朵雲，薄藍色的天啊，妳會不會害羞？應是閒慵的風景，卻身不由己，我望著妳，偷噙淚，回首向北，怒懟微風，斥她太溫柔，說這不是遊子應做的夢，陰翳蠢動，侵吞斗室，從指尖，到字簍，從鼻息，到季風，徬徨漏","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-25T14:50:54.704Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-25T14:52:48.071Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["新詩","創作","隨筆"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"竹河翁","department":"fearlesscharge","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}